 [IPA: [bɐːn]] (German Bern [IPA: [b̥ɛrn]], French Berne [IPA: [bɛʀn]], Italian Berna [IPA: [ˈbɛrna]], Romansh Berna [IPA: [ˈbɛrnə]], Bernese German Bärn [IPA: [b̥æːrn]]), is the "Bundesstadt" (administrative capital) of Switzerland and, with 140,000 people, 
