</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 is the fourth most populous Swiss city (after Zürich, Geneva and Basel).
</PARAGRAPH>

<PARAGRAPH>
Most of 
<REF ID="1018.3" SEMCAT="city" SYNCAT="subj-det">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="name" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" CASE="genitive">Bern's</REFEX>
<ALT-REFEX>
